                        <p>That random Asian girl in the common room without makeup on</p>
<p>P.S. I really am curious about these answers. If you'd like to respond, email me at af192@duke.edu.</p>
<p><em>Amy Fan is a Trinity first-year. Her column, "fangirling" runs on alternate Tuesdays.</em></p>

